profile:
Rosewood Kitchens is a family owned custom cabinetry company, specializing in creating custom kitchen cabinets, washroom vanities, office cabinets, islands, and bars. With a passion for re-modelling spaces, Rosewood Kitchens is committed to creating beautiful spaces for your home and office using only the best quality materials and skilled craftsmanship. Having over 25 years of carpentry experience, we incorporate the use of the latest technologies and hardware, along with rich woods and textures to create a unique space that fits each clientâ€™s needs.

Are You Ready To Make Your Dream Kitchen A Reality? Well, Look No Further! Here At Rosewood Kitchens, Fine Cabinetry Is Revealed As You Look Beyond The Exterior Beauty And Into Its Components, Construction, And Finishing. Every Rosewood Kitchen Cabinet Is Made To Order By Our Skilled Team Members, Whose Focus Is On Crafting Quality Pieces, One Detail At A Time. We Invite You To Explore What Rosewood Kitchens Has To Offer!
